snippet.title: Shisui House - Nyan Nyan Parasol - 2000
snippet.description:
For those who wants to rememorate this Bubble Bobble alternative game based on a anime series that was Nyan Nyan Parasol (also known as ニャンニャンパラソル) developed and published by Shisui House in 2000.
